      "side": 1,
      "message": "I don\u0027t think I would have coded it this way with both parameters being supplied, metricName and dimensionName, and one ignored if it isn\u0027t provided.\n\nI think what I would have done is just have one parameter and have the caller, in this case a method in either DimensionNames or DimensionValues, supply either \"metricName\u003d\" + metricName or \"metricName\u003d\" + metricName + \"dimensionName\u003d\" + dimensionName.",
